---
title: Southwest Beyond Meat® Salad with Corn and Creamy Lime Dressing
description: Southwest spice flavours tender Beyond Meat® and quick-cooking corn in this speedy salad. Want to make it even faster? Leave the tomatoes whole!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1050_W32_CA_RT161328-3_Main_low-d9fd69f9.jpg
